==Matches==
The dates and venues were announced on 23 April.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rugbyworldcup-argentina2023.blogspot.com.br/2014/04/consur-2014-south-american-championship.html|title=Rugby World Cup - Argentina 2023: CONSUR: 2014 South American Championship Dates and Venues|first=Paul|last=Tait|date=23 April 2014|website=rugbyworldcup-argentina2023.blogspot.com.br|accessdate=14 September 2017}}</ref>

